{"tid":1304324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋愧對犧牲的義士！！","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T06:02:50.000Z","uid":274336,"like":125,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0daa944d85efdfa003991154c5ab5776a2b23c","tid":1304324,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"呢幾日嗰嗰係度出膠post！咩寶礦力，pizza hut就有幾千個正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請問正經post去晒邊？<br />\n<br />\n6月9號，6月12號，林鄭出嚟講完嘢，大家都一肚火唔收貨，大家齊上齊落去抗爭！請問依家咩事？<br />\n<br />\n旺角俾狗圍死係咁打；林鄭出嚟講廢話；抗爭post竟然得嗰千幾like！！梁烈士，盧烈士用條生命係想帶咩信息俾我哋？係咪想再有人用自己的生命去點燃返你班友團火！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>義士的生命壓係我哋背上</strong></span></span></span>！！我哋咩都冇爭取到！！<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家重新出發！！如果你團火熄咗，請你重溫返6月9到依家所發生的事！我知大家都好攰！但係我自己依家真係冇面目去拜祭義士！我講唔出原來我乜都未爭取到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3124b72be07d24d0b051f7cf51ad4c3e8da45d","tid":1304324,"uid":265192,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:49:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重啟文宣，反駁「壽終正寢」論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不撤不散，聚焦五大訴求<br />\n停止執著連儂牆，Be Water第日再整過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"175dcc7585b9d4b29a4e125d07739b59cd8901df","tid":1304324,"uid":265192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y89X0ke.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy89X0ke.png&h=5453cdeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8On3brV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8On3brV.png&h=c2b4f58e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2679b23ba183b87df3149e252d046bf9bfb3d67c","tid":1304324,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目前戰線太多，運動重心偏離；大家花太多時間係寶礦力同連儂場上面。[b]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red]我地需要集中火力係五大訴求上面。</span></span></strong>只有個議題仲係度，個運動先繼續有力量做其他野。重心要放返係「送中」上面，連帶反黑警；連儂場唔好太執著、反TVB唔好反多過林鄭。先搞「送中」，燈柱同信用評分先慢慢普及。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重心一定要放返係「送中」上面！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"bba574cd9184a1f86369c624f5f8d407bdc21be0","tid":1304324,"uid":18959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:51:21.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n<br />\n救人<br />\n追究嚴懲黑警<br />\n撤回暴動<br />\n監控燈柱<br />\n信用制度<br />\n雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地有好多野要一步一步爭取啊"},{"pid":"1ddd55de7052779769b96716a40bdfa77eb306c4","tid":1304324,"uid":240534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6fedc381346c6a7f9c345ae195008624bbdf53b","tid":1304324,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"要聚焦真普選同釋放義士呀"},{"pid":"32ffe6a08a43f5780f4097254c550eee2714b0a1","tid":1304324,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"ad43a6fba66d568621cca3aff8974257a7bbde28","tid":1304324,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"五大訴求五大訴求五大訴求五大訴求五大訴求五大訴求"},{"pid":"561d5592d28ee4f74ce789d4b87f8b93cee5cb2e","tid":1304324,"uid":514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"聚焦雙普選呀各位手足"},{"pid":"8d19609106257b7869244a8e4422c5c4e669b5d9","tid":1304324,"uid":147643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"